{"tid":2075353,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖遊戲系列最新作《絕命精神病院實驗》曝光首支預告影片 預計 2021 年問世","createTime":"2020-06-22T20:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T00:40:48.000Z","uid":10063,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bb6f33366fa5b8ec9258abb85915dad4a25edd53","tid":2075353,"uid":10063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T20:02:47.000Z","msg":"Outlast 3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重記得第一次玩第一集果隻心跳加速感覺<br />\n<br />\n加拿大獨立遊戲開發團隊 Red Barrels 於 PC Gaming Show 2020 線上直播曝光旗下恐怖遊戲《絕命精神病院（暫譯，英文原名 Outlast）》系列最新作《絕命精神病院實驗（暫譯，原名：The Outlast Trials）》首支預告影片，預計 2021 年問世。<br />\n <br />\n  《絕命精神病院實驗》並非《絕命精神病院》前兩集的續作，而是採用同一個世界觀，為單人或多人合作遊戲，玩家將扮演實驗的受害者，除了可以獨自遊玩面對外，也可選擇與其他至多三個被迫成為實驗對象的玩家合作遊玩，而目前研發團隊尚未公開玩家到底將面臨何種恐怖情境。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/35/2769981c2ea6b9eb627e8d391018vaz5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F35%2F2769981c2ea6b9eb627e8d391018vaz5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=8d93587d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n  遊戲故事背景設定在冷戰時期，不情願的志工被莫科夫公司（Murkoff Corporation）強迫招募，成為新型洗腦和精神控制方法的受試者。在佈滿猜疑、恐懼和暴力的世界裡，你的道德會面臨挑戰、你的耐力會遭到試驗，而你的理智會被粉碎。<br />\n <br />\n  遊戲於 2019 年底公開後至今有了進一步消息，官方正式釋出《絕命精神病院實驗》遊戲預告影片，玩家將以第一人稱視角並與朋友合作，試著逃離這恐怖的地方。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n另外小弟有個香港本土恐怖遊戲YT Channel, 有興趣既黎支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/c/魚佬9CFamily\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2F%E9%AD%9A%E4%BD%AC9CFamily&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7vkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=83342cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/c/魚佬9CFamily</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjuSzXt.jpg&amp;h=e395ac1f&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"7da988788e36e112c0b2ba0e61f4b12e91f95e06","tid":2075353,"uid":10063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T20:06:27.000Z","msg":"《絕命精神病院實驗》系列新作要再次挑戰你恐懼的極限 預計 2021 年問世<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QzlzyIPlK9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQzlzyIPlK9I&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7vkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=80381bac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QzlzyIPlK9I</a>"},{"pid":"a18eb3b7f12aead53ab4f989c6bad98805acd005","tid":2075353,"uid":37666,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T22:18:57.000Z","msg":"Outlast2都麻麻地<br />\n3都係睇定啲先"},{"pid":"66b19124a2ea4e1998ac55899f21da1e64349552","tid":2075353,"uid":36432,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T22:24:54.000Z","msg":"劇本：主角一開始就俾人打撚死咗，要你用個兇手玩足成隻Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13de1f126c35f07f1fd1e9b1676ca3f448ddf509","tid":2075353,"uid":10063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a18eb3b7f12aead53ab4f989c6bad98805acd005","tid":2075353,"uid":37666,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T22:18:57.000Z","msg":"Outlast2都麻麻地<br />\n3都係睇定啲先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T22:28:51.000Z","msg":"你岩，1 最好玩， 2 開始變質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bc78b02c08b03a2ad27fb8ccf623656fd81078","tid":2075353,"uid":37666,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"66b19124a2ea4e1998ac55899f21da1e64349552","tid":2075353,"uid":36432,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T22:24:54.000Z","msg":"劇本：主角一開始就俾人打撚死咗，要你用個兇手玩足成隻Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T22:31:08.000Z","msg":"你錯了<br />\n要先比你用主角一段時間<br />\n同玩家建立感情先<b